            "clubDetailsButton": "Club Details",
            "noClubsText": "<h4 class=\"club-list-item-new__title\" style=\"color: #0070c0; margin: 0px 0px 1rem;\">Didn't find a club in your area?</h4>\n<p><span style=\"color: #4a4a4a;\">Leave us your information and we'll notify you when a club opens near you. </span></p>",
            "noClubsTrialText": "<h5 class=\"club-list-item-new__title\" style=\"color: #0070c0; margin: 0px 0px 1rem;\">Didn't find a club in your area?</h5>\n<p>Expand your range on this form or view all of our clubs in the <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=D13FFCCC6DC444398372DC1ADECB3A55&amp;_z=z\">Club Finder</a>. Or, you can leave us your information and we'll notify you when a club opens near you.</p>",
            "clubFinderNoClubsWelcomeText": "Thank you! Your information will help us find a way to start a new club in your area. While we work on that, you can still j<a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=7CF1233B9FBB4754953D46DCBA7E2AE9&amp;_z=z\">oin USMS</a> and take advantage of our other benefits, like our <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=DD2770365EBF4239958D3E4714618338&amp;_z=z\">Workout Library</a>, <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=3FA347493E71415F804C86C089A59638&amp;_z=z\">in-person and virtual events</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=603B158E3D714F219023EDF96CE337FB&amp;_z=z\">exclusive content</a>, <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=8523952D43214351A74CA730A9B4CA54&amp;_z=z\">partner discounts</a>, and <a href=\"community.usms.org\">online community</a>.",
            "trialMembershipNoClubsWelcomeText": "<p>Thank you! Your information will help us find a way to start a new program in your area. While we work on that, you can view all of our clubs using the <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=D13FFCCC6DC444398372DC1ADECB3A55&amp;_z=z\">Club Finder</a>&nbsp;tool or review some of our other <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=F41F7478256E4B5E8E244645A7EE6BA3&amp;_z=z\">benefits</a>&nbsp;that can help you find <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=DD2770365EBF4239958D3E4714618338&amp;_z=z\">workouts</a>&nbsp;and a <a href=\"~/link.aspx?_id=A0AA51AA8E8A4B22A5C5D278F8A4F0F4&amp;_z=z\">community</a>&nbsp;virtually.&nbsp;</p>",
